{
  "stem": "25639.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I used to be sent by my mother, by myself, and on my bicycle, and there was a-- a live chicken in a basket.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And I would bicycle into Beregszasz and have the chicken slaughtered on Thursdays, so that on Shabbat-- on Friday, my mother could cook it for Shabbat.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, goodness.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we really sang a lot.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The boys played various games.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Chess was a big, big game among the men.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I would watch and-- you're too little yet, I was told.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- I-- but-- I-- I learned how to move the pieces before they started teaching me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] But I stopped playing chess when my children started beating me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] They played with walnuts.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] Lots of walnuts grew in our area.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there was a game-- they would line up the walnuts, and then they would use another walnut to knock off the walnuts.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So usually from right to left, and depending on where-- where that walnut would go through, if it went through, the-- the player would win the walnuts that was cut off to the right.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So my brothers would bring home more walnuts, and mother said, that's all I need is more walnuts.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Here I'm trying to give them away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There was so much, usually into the next season.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we did, very often, give away things that we grew and that we had plenty of.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We had fruit orchards, as well, and apples, oranges, pears, and currants.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was really a very rich area near the Carpathian Mountains, and the dark soil would fertilize it each-- each spring as it washed down into the fields.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we-- we didn't sell them, no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We-- we-- usually Mother made-- they bottled it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's canning here, but we bottled it.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
